.title Developer Services

These services provide a vast array of tools for the professional 
developer.  Through an active relationship with partners such as
Intel and SunSoft, SCO provides a wide variety of the latest
programming tools and development environments, including C, C++,
and Java.

Developer Services: 

  SCO Universal Developer Kit - C and C++ development tools
  SCO Java Development Kit    - Java development tools
  Java Workshop from Sun      - Integrated Java development
                                environment
 
